com.interface21.web.servlet.i18n
Class CookieLocaleResolver

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.interface21.web.servlet.i18n.CookieLocaleResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
LocaleResolver
public class CookieLocaleResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements LocaleResolver

Implementation of LocaleResolver that uses a cookie sent back to the user in case of a custom setting, with a fallback to the accept header locale. This is especially useful for stateless applications without user sessions.

Custom controllers can thus override the user's locale by calling setLocale, e.g. responding to a certain locale change request.

Since:
27.02.2003
